yers%20based%20in%20Bengaluru%20may%20not%20have%20the%20same%20option%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20disadvantage%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%20severe%20backlash%2C%20the%20bill%20has%20now%20been%20put%20on%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721281500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fpmtu748o_sameer-nigam_625x300_18_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fphonepe-ceo-sameer-nigam-slams-karnatakas-job-quota-bill-6130753%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bill%20mandated%20reserving%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20management-level%20jobs%20and%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20non-management-level%20jobs%20for%20locals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fphonepe-ceo-sameer-nigam-slams-karnatakas-job-quota-bill-6130753%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fphonepe-ceo-sameer-nigam-slams-karnatakas-job-quota-bill-6130753%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fphonepe-ceo-sameer-nigam-slams-karnatakas-job-quota-bill-6130753%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Year%20After%20NCP%20Split%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20Struggles%20To%20Stop%20Exodus%20To%20Uncle's%20Camp%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20is%20in%20a%20huddle%20with%20party%20colleagues%20in%20Pune%20today%20after%20several%20key%20leaders%20switched%20to%20the%20NCP%20faction%20led%20by%20his%20uncle%20and%20party%20founder%20Sharad%20Pawar.%20Four%20Pune%20leaders%20resigned%20from%20their%20roles%20in%20the%20NCP%20faction%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20joined%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20camp%20yesterday.%20These%20include%20Ajit%20Gavhane%2C%20NCP's%20former%20Pimpri-Chinchwad%20chief%2C%20and%20local%20leaders%20Rahul%20Bhosale%2C%20Pankaj%20Bhalekar%2C%20and%20Yash%20Sane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2020%20former%20corporators%2C%20mayors%20and%20unit%20heads%20from%20Pimpri-Chinchwad%20switched%20to%20the%20senior%20Pawar's%20camp%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20switch%20comes%20a%20month%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20in%20which%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20posted%20a%20stellar%20show%20by%20winning%208%20of%20the%2010%20seats%20it%20contested.%20The%20Ajit%20Pawar%20camp%20was%20left%20disappointed%2C%20as%20it%20managed%20to%20win%20just%20one%20seat%20and%20lost%20three.%20The%20results%2C%20at%20one%20level%2C%20also%20showed%20it%20is%20the%20senior%20Pawar%20that%20NCP%20supporters%20are%20eager%20to%20back.%20This%20is%20all%20the%20more%20significant%20because%20state%20polls%20in%20Maharashtra%20are%20months%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESharad%20Pawar's%20Comeback%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%2C%20who%20founded%20NCP%20in%201999%2C%20suffered%20a%20big%20setback%20last%20year%20when%20his%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%20led%20a%20mutiny%20and%20joined%20the%20Shiv%20Sena-BJP%20government%20as%20a%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20veteran%20politician%20also%20lost%20his%20party's%20name%20and%20symbol%20and%20had%20to%20fight%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20under%20the%20name%20of%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar).%20The%20poll%20results%20brought%20good%20news%20as%20the%20veteran%20trumped%20his%20nephew's%20faction%20and%20won%20eight%20seats%20out%20of%20the%2010%20NCP%20(SP)%20contested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20NCP%20Leaders%20Are%20Switching%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20in%20Maharashtra%20are%20months%20away%2C%20and%20every%20leader%20is%20exploring%20ways%20to%20get%20a%20poll%20pass.%20With%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20faction%20scoring%20big%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20many%20leaders%20expect%20them%20to%20repeat%20it%20in%20the%20state%20election%20and%20want%20to%20be%20on%20the%20winning%20side.%20Several%20leaders%20have%20cited%20local%20factors%20behind%20their%20move%20to%20switch.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20Pimpri-Chinchwad%2C%20both%20Ajit%20dada%20and%20Pawar%20sahab%20contributed%20to%20its%20development.%20But%20since%202017%2C%20BJP%20has%20been%20ruling%20the%20municipal%20corporation.%20Development%20work%20here%20was%20done%20in%20the%20wrong%20way.%20There%20was%20rampant%20corruption%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gavhane%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar's%20daughter%20and%20four-time%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20said%20the%20veteran%20leader%20has%20been%20working%20for%20development%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20last%2060%20years.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20faith%20in%20Pawar%20sahab's%20ideology%20and%20many%20people%20in%20the%20opposition%2C%20too%2C%20look%20towards%20him%20with%20great%20hopes.%20This%20is%20why%20people%20are%20joining%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sule%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20Ajit%20Pawar%20Switch%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20leaders%20of%20his%20faction%20switch%20to%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20camp%2C%20there%20is%20speculation%20that%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20too%2C%20may%20finally%20try%20to%20go%20back.%20Sharad%20Pawar%20was%20recently%20asked%20if%20his%20nephew%20will%20get%20a%20place%20in%20his%20party%20if%20he%20wants%20to%20return.%20The%20veteran%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BSuch%20decisions%20cannot%20be%20taken%20at%20the%20personal%20level.%20My%20colleagues%20who%20stood%20by%20me%20during%20the%20crisis%20will%20be%20asked%20first%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar's%20standing%20in%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20government%20has%20taken%20a%20big%20blow%20due%20to%20his%20poll%20setback.%20He%20is%20now%20a%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20whose%20party%20managed%20just%20one%20seat%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20contest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20against%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20upcoming%20state%20polls%20will%20be%20a%20tall%20challenge%20fo