ng%20local%20farmers%20over%20a%20land%20dispute%20in%20Pune%20district's%20Mulshi%20village.%20The%20footage%2C%20which%20has%20sparked%20public%20outrage%2C%20shows%20her%20in%20a%20heated%20exchange%20with%20a%20farmer%2C%20demanding%20to%20see%20land%20documents%20allegedly%20in%20her%20name.%20As%20tensions%20escalated%2C%20she%20waved%20the%20firearm%20threateningly%20before%20quickly%20concealing%20it%20upon%20noticing%20a%20camera%20recording%20the%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20video%20went%20viral%2C%20the%20Pune%20Police%20took%20action%2C%20registering%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20against%20her.%20The%20FIR%20also%20names%20her%20husband%2C%20Dilip%20Khedkar%2C%20a%20retired%20administrative%20officer%2C%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDilip%20Khedkar%20also%20faces%20a%20history%20of%20corruption%20charges%2C%20having%20been%20suspended%20twice%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20a%20government%20officer.%20His%20first%20suspension%20occurred%20in%202018%20while%20serving%20as%20the%20Regional%20Officer%20in%20Kolhapur.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20the%20local%20sawmill%20and%20timber%20merchants%20association%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20him%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20demanded%20bribes%20ranging%20from%20Rs%2025%2C000%20to%20Rs%2050%2C000%20to%20restore%20their%20power%20and%20water%20supplies.%20He%20faced%20another%20suspension%20in%202020%20due%20to%20similar%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Khedkar%20family's%20troubles%20extend%20beyond%20this%20incident.%20Puja%20Khedkar%2C%20who%20secured%20an%20all-India%20rank%20(AIR)%20of%20841%20in%20the%20UPSC%20exam%20as%20part%20of%20the%202023%20batch%2C%20has%20faced%20allegations%20of%20making%20false%20claims%20in%20her%20UPSC%20candidature%20and%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20misusing%20her%20power%20after%20assuming%20her%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllegations%20against%20her%20include%20misrepresentation%20as%20an%20OBC