pecific%20scrutiny%20on%20key%20constituencies%20like%20Ayodhya%20and%20Amethi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20underscores%20a%20significant%20decline%20of%208%25%20in%20the%20BJP's%20vote%20share%20across%20all%20regions%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20It%20calls%20on%20the%20central%20leadership%20to%20take%20decisive%20action%20to%20prevent%20future%20elections%20from%20being%20reduced%20to%20a%20contest%20between%20advantaged%20and%20disadvantaged%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20UP%20BJP%20President%20Bhupendra%20Chaudhary%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%20met%20with%20senior%20party%20leaders.%20Further%20discussions%20with%20leaders%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20planned%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20strategy%20revision%20following%20the%20party's%20electoral%20setbacks%20in%20the%20crucial%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeculation%20regarding%20internal%20strife%20among%20state%20party%20leaders%20intensified%20after%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20attributed%20the%20electoral%20reverses%20to%20%26quot%3Bover-confidence%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20rebutted%20by%20his%20deputy%20Keshav%20Maurya.%20He%20said%20the%20party%20and%20the%20organisation%20are%20bigger%20than%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20unit's%20report%20identifies%20six%20primary%20reasons%20for%20the%20BJP's%20subdued%20performance%2C%20including%20perceived%20administrative%20high-handedness%2C%20discontent%20among%20party%20workers%2C%20frequent%20paper%20leaks%2C%20and%20the%20employment%20of%20contractual%20workers%20in%20government%20positions%2C%20which%20allegedly%20reinforced%20opposition%20narratives%20about%20the%20party's%20stance%20on%20reservations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20MLA%20has%20no%20power.%20The%20District%20Magistrate%20and%20adhikaris%20(officials)%20rule%20the%20roost.%20This%20is%20making%20our%20workers%20feel%20humiliated.%20For%20years%2C%20the%20RSS%20and%20BJP%20have%20worked%20together%2C%20building%20strong%20connections%20in%20society.%20Officials%20cannot%20replace%20party%20workers%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20party%20leader%20said.%20The%20RSS%20is%20the%20BJP's%20ideological%20mentor%20and%20is%20credited%20with%20building%20the%20party's%20base%20from%20the%20ground%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20leader%20pointed%20out%20that%20at%20least%2015%20paper%20leaks%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years%20alone%20in%20the%20state%20had%20led%20to%20amplification%20of%20the%20opposition's%20narrative%20that%20the%20BJP%20wanted%20to%20stall%20reservations.%20%26quot%3BOn%20top%20of%20that%2C%20government%20jobs%20were%20being%20filled%20up%20by%20contractual%20workers%2C%20which%20only%20strengthened%20the%20opposition's%20misleading%20narrative%20about%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20President%20JP%20Nadda%2C%20after%20attending%20a%20state%20executive%20meeting%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20consulted%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20Bhupendra%20Chaudhary%2C%20and%20other%20key%20leaders%20to%20address%20these%20issues%20systematically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20these%20matters%20have%20to%20be%20discussed%20at%20length%2C%20they%20are%20calling%20state%20leaders%20in%20batches%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BJP%20functionary%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20notes%20shifts%20in%20electoral%20support%2C%20citing%20diminished%20backing%20from%20the%20Kurmi%20and%20Maurya%20communities%2C%20and%20a%20reduction%20in%20Dalit%20votes.%20It%20acknowledges%20the%20decreased%20vote%20share%20of%20Mayawati's%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20and%20the%20Congress's%20improved%20performance%20in%20certain%20regions%20as%20additional%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20it%20has%20been%20highlighted%20to%20the%20BJP's%20central%20leadership%20that%20the%20state%20unit%20must%20resolve%20its%20differences%20promptly%20and%20start%C2%A0%20commence%20grassroots%20work%20to%20prevent%20the%20sentiment%20from%20evolving%20into%20an%20%26quot%3Bagada%20versus%20pichada%26quot%3B%20(upper%20caste%20versus%20backward%20castes)%20conflict.%20Once%20known%20as%20a%20party%20favoured%20by%20the%20OBCs%2C%20the%20UP%20BJP%2C%20under%20former%20chief%20minister%20Kalyan%20Singh%2C%20had%20claimed%20the%20support%20of%20the%20Lodh%20community%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20but%20the%20support%20among%20OBCs%20for%20the%20BJP%20surged%20under%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%202014.%20%26quot%3BThe%20winning%20streak%20of%202014%2C%202017%2C%202019%20and%202022%20should%20not%20be%20undermined.%20The%20senior%20leaders%20need%20to%20intervene%20and%20provide%20guidance.%20The%20state%20must%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20adhering%20to%20central%20directives.%20We%20are%20all%20equals%3B%20no%20one%20should%20assume%20a%20dominant%20role.%20Leaders%20must%20comprehend%20UP's%20local%20issues%2C%20and%20efforts%20must%20be%20made%20to%20boost%20morale%20among%20workers%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20party%20official%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20indicates%20that%20the%20Kurmi%20and%20Maurya%20castes%20drifted%20away%20from%20the%20BJP%20this%20time%2C%20and%20the%20party%20only%20managed%20to%20secure%20one%20third%20of%20the%20Dalit%20votes.%20It%20further%20highlighted%20that%20the%20BSP's%20vote%20share%20decreased%20by%2010%20per%20cent%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20improved%20its%20standing%20in%20three%20regions%20of%20UP%2C%20influencing%20the%20overall%20results.%20The%20state%20unit%20also%20observed%20that%20the%20party's%20campaign%20peaked%20early%20due%20to%20the%20rapid%20distribution%20of%20tickets.%20By%20the%20sixth%20and%20seventh%20phases%2C%20fatigue%20had%20set%20in%20among%20workers%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%20Statements%20by%20party%20leaders%20against%20reservation%20policies%20further%20exacerbated%20the%20party's%20diminishing%20support.%20%26quot%3BIssues%20such%20as%20the%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%20resonated%20with%20senior%20citizens%2C%20while%20concerns%20like%20Agniveer%20and%20paper%20leaks%20resonated%20with%20the%20youth%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20unit%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20opposition%20effectively%20raised%20issues%20that%20resonated%20with%20the%20people.%20They%20have%20called%20for%20party%20workers%20to%20be%20treated%20with%20respect%2C%20and%20efforts%20are%20underway%20from%20the%20central%20BJP%20to%20ensure%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20secured%2037%20of%20the%2080%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20up%20from%20five%20in%202019.%20The%20BJP%20was%20reduced%20to%2033%20seats%2C%20down%20from%2062%2C%20resulting%20in%20an%20overall%20decline%20in%20the%20party's%20national%20tally.%20The%20UP%20outcome%20has%20stunned%20the%20leadership%20that%20had%20anticipated%20significant%20gains%20from%20a%20state%20where%20the%20Ram%20temple's%20grand%20consecration%20ceremony%20was%20held%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20party's%20own%20data%2C%20its%20weakest%20performances%20were%20in%20the%20west%20and%20Kashi%20(Varanasi)%20regions%2C%20where%20it%20won%20just%20eight%20of%20the%2028%20seats.%20In%20Braj%20(western%20UP)%2C%20the%20party%20won%20eight%20out%20of%2013%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Gorakhpur%2C%20the%20stronghold%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20the%20BJP%20managed%20only%20six%20of%2013%20seats%2C%20while%20in%20Awadh%20(region%20that%20includes%20Lucknow%2C%20Ayodhya%2C%20Faizabad)%2C%20it%20won%20just%20seven%20of%2016.%20In%20Kanpur-Bundelkhand%2C%20the%20BJP%20failed%20to%20reclaim%20its%20previous%20seats%2C%20securing%20only%20four%20out%20of%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogi%20Adityanath%20attributed%20the%20poor%20results%20to%20overconfidence%2C%20while%20his%20deputy%20Keshav%20Maurya%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20strengthening%20the%20party%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20central%20leadership%20has%20instructed%20state%20leaders%20to%20resolve%20their%20differences%20and%20concentrate%20on%20the%20upcoming%20by-elections%20for%2010%20assembly%20seats%20vacated%20due%20to%20various%20reasons%2C%20including%20MLAs%20elected%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20no%20change%20in%20leadership%20until%20then.%20They%20have%20asked%20us%20to%20fix%20things%20and%20advised%20against%20complaints%20at%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20quoted%20above%20remarked%2C%20adding%20that%20senior%20party%20leaders%20would%20undertake%20a%20statewide%20tour%20to%20different%20constituencies%20to%20connect%20with%20voters%20and%20mitigate%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Anupriya%20Patel%2C%20a%20BJP%20ally%2C%20wrote%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20flagging%20the%20delay%20in%20filling%20quotas%20for%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20in%20state%20government%20jobs.%20Ms%20Patel's%20Apna%20Dal%20has%20influence%20specifically%20among%20Kurmis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupporters%20of%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20contend%20that%20the%20chief%20minister's%20command%20over%20the%20state's%20administration%2C%20coupled%20with%20his%20focus%20on%20stringent%20law%20and%20order%20and%20discipline%2C%20helped%20the%20BJP%20maintain%20its%20grip%20on%20the%20state.%20%26quot%3BThe%20main%20issue%20was%20the%20repetition%20of%20unpopular%20candidates%2C%20which%20should%20have%20been%20avoided.%20Baba%20(Yogi%20Adityanath)%20had%20no%20role%20in%20ticket%20allocation.%20As%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20who%20has%20demonstrated%20his%20popularity%20by%20returning%20to%20power%2C%20his%20integrity%20and%20commitment%20are%20beyond%20doubt.%20The%20central%20leadership%20recognises%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20MLA%20close%20to%20Mr%20Adityanath%20affirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721279160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F9pd390u8_modi-yogi_625x300_18_June_24.jpg%22%