tortion%20Complaints%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDilip%20Khedkar%2C%20a%20retired%20Maharashtra%20government%20officer%20and%20father%20of%20trainee%20IAS%20officer%20Puja%20Khedkar%2C%20was%20suspended%20twice%20on%20charges%20of%20corruption.%20Dilip%20Khedkar%20is%20on%20the%20run%20after%20a%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20him%20and%20his%20wife%20Manorama%20Khedkar%20after%20a%20video%20of%20the%20latter%20threatening%20some%20people%20with%20a%20gun%20went%20viral.%20The%20Pune%20Anti%20Corruption%20Bureau%20has%20also%20initiated%20a%20probe%20against%20him%20after%20a%20complaint%20that%20his%20assets%20were%20disproportionate%20to%20his%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDilip%20Khedkar%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20faced%20suspension%20in%202018%20and%20in%202020.%20Documents%20accessed%20by%20NDTV%20show%20that%20at%20least%20300%20small%20businessmen%20had%20complained%20against%20Dilip%20Khedkar%20in%202015%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20causing%20%26quot%3Bunnecessary%20trouble%26quot%3B%20and%20extortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20when%20Dilip%20Khedkar%20was%20working%20as%20Regional%20Officer%2C%20Kolhapur%2C%20the%20local%20saw%20mill%20and%20timber%20merchants%20association%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20him%2C%20alleging%20he%20had%20demanded%20bribes%20ranging%20from%20Rs%2025%2C000%20to%20Rs%2050%2C000%20to%20restore%20their%20power%20and%20water%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20mentions%20that%20Dilip%20Khedkar%20was%20on%20one%20occasion%20absent%20for%20six%20to%20seven%20months%20without%20permission.%C2%A0A%20complaint%20dated%202019%20accused%20Dilip%20Khedkar%20of%20demanding%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20from%20a%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202020%20order%20says%20Dilip%20Khedkar%20was%20suspended%20under%20Rule%203(1)%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20Civil%20Services%20(Conduct)%20Rules%2C%201979%20and%20sub-section%201(a)%20of%20Rule%20No.%204%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20Civil%20Services%20(Discipline%20and%20Appeal)%20Rules%2C%201979%20and%20the%20Maharashtra%20Water%20(Prevention%20and%20Control%20of%20Pollution)%20Act%2C%201983.%20The%20order%20cited%20multiple%20complaint%20against%20him%20and%20also%20said%20an%20inquiry%20had%20been%20launched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Khedkars'%20assets%20have%20come%20under%20the%20spotlight%20amid%20the%20investigation%20against%2034-year-old%20Puja%20Khedkar%2C%20whose%20selection%20as%20an%20IAS%20officer%20has%20raised%20many%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20ACB%20complaint%20has%20flagged%20the%20land%2C%20cars%20and%20companies%20owned%20by%20Dilip%20Khedkar.%20The%20retired%20officer%20was%20questioned%20for%20three%20days%20before%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20became%20unreachable.%20Police%20are%20now%20looking%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prelude%20to%20the%20Khedkars'%20trouble%20was%20a%20complaint%20by%20Pune%20district%20collector%20Suhas%20Diwase%20wrote%20to%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Secretary%20Sujata%20Saunik%20about%20trainee%20IAS%20officer%20Puja%20Khedkar's%20demands%20for%20perks%20she%20was%20not%20entitled%20to.%20It%20soon%20came%20to%20light%20that%20she%20was%20selected%20as%20an%20IAS%20officer%20after%20she%20claimed%20reservation%20as%20a%20person%20with%20disability%20and%20an%20OBC%20candidate.%20She%20didn't%20turn%20up%20for%20a%20medical%20check-up%20to%20verify%20her%20disability%20claim%20and%20submitted%20a%20private%20facility's%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPuja%20Khedkar%20had%20sought%20reservation%20benefits%20as%20an%20OBC%20candidate%20from%20the%20non-creamy%20layer%20--%20a%20candidate%20qualifies%20for%20OBC%20reservation%20if%20his%2Fher%20annual%20family%20income%20is%20lower%20than%208%20lakh.%20But%20RTI%20activist%20Vijay%20Kumbhar%20has%20pointed%20out%20Dilip%20Khedkar's%20affidavits%20filed%20before%20he%20contested%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20show%20that%20he%20has%20assets%20worth%20Rs%2040%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHer%20father%2C%20Dilip%20Khedkar%2C%20in%20his%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20affidavit%20showed%20a%20conservative%20estimated%20wealth%20of%20Rs%2040%20crores%20and%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20Rs%2049%20lakh.%20The%20information%20is%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumbhar%20said%2C%20according%20to%20a%20PTI%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20now%20ordered%20an%20investigation%20into%20Puja%20Khedkar's%20selection%20into%20IAS%20and%20her%20training%20has%20been%20put%20on%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721277120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F04b5jflo_puja-khedkar-father-split_625x300_18_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpuja-khedkar-dilip-khedkar-puja-khedkars-father-was-suspended-twice-on-extortion-complaints-6130333%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dilip%20Khedkar%2C%20a%20retired%20Maharashtra%20government%20officer%20and%20father%20of%20trainee%20IAS%20officer%20Puja%20Khedkar%2C%20was%20suspended%20twice%20on%20charges%20of%20corruption.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpuja-khedkar-dilip-khedkar-puja-khedkars-father-was-suspended-twice-on-extortion-complaints-6130333%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpuja-khedkar-dilip-khedkar-puja-khedkars-father-was-suspended-twice-on-extortion-complaints-6130333%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpuja-khedkar-dilip-khedkar-puja-khedkars-father-was-suspended-twice-on-extortion-complaints-6130333%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20VP%20pick%20Vance%20vows%20to%20fight%20for%20'forgotten'%20Americans%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721277104000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fbead%2Flive%2Fcc9dd8f0-44b9-11ef-9e1c-3b4a473456a6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F