%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESen.%20JD%20Vance%20of%20Ohio%20gave%20the%20keynote%20speech%20for%20the%20third%20day%20of%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Wong%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESen.%20JD%20Vance%20of%20Ohio%20gave%20his%20high-profile%20VP%20acceptance%20speech%20on%20Wednesday%20night%20at%20the%20RNC.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDonald%20Trump%20made%20Vance%20his%20VP%20pick%2C%20anointing%20a%20MAGA%20heir%20apparent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EVance%20repeatedly%20referenced%20the%20three%20key%20battleground%20states%20of%C2%A0Pennsylvania%2C%20Michigan%2C%20and%20Wisconsin.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESen.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-vice-president-jd-vance-career-facts-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJD%20Vance%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Ohio%20on%20Wednesday%20railed%20against%20decades%20of%20American%20policy%20in%20his%20major%20national%20moment%20as%20the%20Republican%20vice%20presidential%20nominee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Vance%20underlined%20a%20populist%20Republican%20Party%20to%20the%20point%20that%20he%20came%20out%20to%20a%20Merle%20Haggard%20hit%20that%20was%20written%20in%20protest%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Iraq.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20Iraq%20to%20Afghanistan%2C%20from%20the%20financial%20crisis%20to%20the%20great%20recession%2C%20from%20open%20borders%20to%20stagnating%20wages%2C%20the%20people%20who%20govern%20this%20country%20have%20failed%20and%20failed%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Vance%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20until%20a%20guy%20named%20Donald%20J.%20Trump%20came%20along.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%2C%20of%20course%2C%20President%20George%20W.%20Bush%2C%20a%20Republican%2C%20who%20championed%20the%20Iraq%20War.%20Vance%20also%20tore%20into%20NAFTA%2C%20a%20bipartisan%20trade%20deal%20negotiated%20by%20GOP%20President%20George%20H.W.%20Bush%20a