the%20race%2C%20urging%20him%20to%20%26quot%3Bpass%20the%20torch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20a%20pair%20of%20reports%20from%20ABC%20News%20and%20the%20Washington%20Post%20that%20Senate%20Majority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20and%20House%20Minority%20Leader%20Hakeem%20Jeffries%20had%20warned%20Biden%20in%20private%20conversations%20last%20week%20about%20the%20risk%20his%20continued%20candidacy%20posed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20told%20the%20leaders%20he%20was%20the%20nominee%20of%20the%20party%20and%20planned%20to%20win%2C%20White%20House%20spokesman%20Andrew%20Bates%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20Still%2C%20both%20joined%20forces%20in%20the%20following%20days%20to%20lobby%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Committee%20against%20a%20July%20virtual%20roll%20call%20that%20would%20have%20cemented%20Biden's%20nomination%20and%20effectively%20terminated%20efforts%20to%20replace%20him%20atop%20the%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20stoked%20the%20melodrama%20even%20more%20by%20suggesting%20in%20a%20BET%20interview%20taped%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20would%20consider%20dropping%20out%20of%20the%20race%20if%20new%20health%20issues%20emerged.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Senator%20Bernie%20Sanders%2C%20a%20defender%20of%20the%20president%2C%20conceded%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20New%20Yorker%20that%20Biden%20had%20trouble%20completing%20sentences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20worse%2C%20Biden's%20struggles%20played%20out%20against%20scenes%20from%20the%20GOP%20convention%2C%20where%20Republican%20candidate%20Donald%20Trump%20appeared%20on%20stage%20for%20a%20walk-through%20sporting%20a%20bandaged%20ear%20from%20the%20unsuccessful%20assassination%20attempt%20he%20survived%20last%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20defiant%2C%20fist-pumping%20response%20to%20the%20shooting%20proved%20instantly%20iconic%2C%20galvanizing%20voices%20of%20doubt%20within%20the%20Republican%20Party%20behind%20his%20cause.%20On%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20former%20primary%20foes%20