cused%20largely%20on%20Biden's%20rhetoric%20and%20questions%20about%20his%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometime%20come%20and%20talk%20to%20me%20about%20what%20we%20should%20be%20talking%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20told%20NBC%20anchor%20Lester%20Holt%20at%20the%20conclusion.%20%26quot%3BOK%3F%20The%20issues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20resumed%20campaign%20events%20Tuesday%20with%20an%20appearance%20at%20the%20NAACP's%20national%20convention%2C%20but%20quickly%20bungled%20the%20centrepiece%20of%20his%20speech%3A%20a%20new%20proposal%20to%20cap%20rent%20increases%20by%20corporate%20landlords%20at%205%25%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Biden%20appeared%20to%20struggle%20to%20read%20his%20teleprompter%2C%20eventually%20saying%20the%20limit%20would%20be%20%2455.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedical%20Condition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20event%2C%20BET%20News%20released%20excerpts%20from%20an%20interview%20with%20Biden%20where%20he%20appeared%20to%20open%20the%20door%20to%20reconsidering%20his%20reelection%20bid%20if%20doctors%20advised%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20had%20some%20medical%20condition%20that%20emerged%2C%20if%20somebody%2C%20if%20doctors%20came%20to%20me%20and%20said%2C%20you%20got%20this%20problem%20and%20that%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20things%20didn't%20improve.%20Biden%20held%20a%20call%20with%20Jeffrey%20Katzenberg%2C%20the%20Hollywood%20executive%20leading%20his%20fundraising%20effort%2C%20and%20was%20told%20that%20donations%20were%20drying%20up%20over%20concerns%20about%20his%20age%2C%20Semafor%20reported.%20Katzenberg%20subsequently%20issued%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20outlet%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bmisread%20of%20a%20private%20meeting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20then%20went%20to%20tape%20a%20radio%20interview%20with%20Univision%20but%20left%20it%20feeling%20unwell.%20A%20Covid%20test%20confirmed%