esofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111822138.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJoe%20and%20Anthony%20Russo%20are%20in%20talks%20to%20direct%20two%20upcoming%20'Avengers'%20films%20with%20Marvel%20Studios.%20Known%20for%20helming%20four%20MCU%20films%20including%20'Captain%20America%3A%20The%20Winter%20Soldier'%2C%20'Captain%20America%3A%20Civil%20War'%2C%20'Avengers%3A%20Infinity%20War'%20and%20'Avengers%3A%20Endgame'%2C%20their%20films%20have%20collectively%20grossed%20%246.681%20billion.%20Should%20they%20come%20on%20board%2C%20the%20Russos%20confront%20challenges%20including%20'The%20Kang%20Dynasty'%20following%20Jonathan%20Majors'%20exit%20and%20the%20highly%20anticipated%20film%20'Secret%20Wars'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Frusso-brothers-to-make-marvel-return-duo-in-talks-to-direct-avengers-5-and-avengers-secret-wars%2Farticleshow%2F111822138.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI'm%20A%20Nepo%20Kid%2C%26quot%3B%20Admits%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20But%20Calls%20It%20%26quot%3BDouble-Edged%20Sword%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20and%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20President%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20addressed%20his%20status%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bnepotism%20kid%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20podcast%20with%20news%20agency%20ANI.%20As%20the%20son%20of%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20undivided%20LJP%2C%20Mr%20Paswan%20acknowledged%20his%20privilege%20but%20also%20highlighted%20the%20inherent%20challenges%20of%20being%20the%20son%20of%20an%20influential%20political%20leader.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Paswan%2C%20who%20serves%20as%20the%20Union%20Minister%20of%20Food%20Processing%20Industries%20in%20Modi%203.0%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20nepo%20kid%2C%20I%20can't%20shy%20away%20from%20that%20fact.%20I%20am%20proud%20that%20I%20am%20the%20son%20of%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20pride.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20do%20good%20work%2C%20people%20say%20that%20it%20is%20because%20of%20your%20parents.%20So%20the%20credit%20is%20not%20yours.%20But%20if%20you%20do%20bad%2C%20then%20you%20will%20hear%20abuses.%20So%20you%20are%20always%20on%20a%20double-edged%20sword%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20privileged%20position%20as%20the%20son%20of%20a%20party%20leader%2C%20Mr%20Paswan%20claimed%20that%20his%20rise%20to%20the%20party's%20leadership%20was%20not%20automatic.%20He%20had%20to%20prove%20himself%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20split%20within%20the%20LJP%20orchestrated%20by%20his%20uncle%2C%20Pashupati%20Paras.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Paras%2C%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan's%20brother%2C%20was%20the%20MP%20from%20Hajipur%2C%20a%20constituency%20with%20a%20strong%20Paswan%20vote%20bank.%20However%2C%20the%20last%20assembly%20polls%20indicated%20that%20the%206%20per%20cent%20Paswan%20vote%20had%20consolidated%20behind%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20a%20factor%20the%20BJP%20considered%20when%20excluding%20Pashupati%20Paras%20from%20the%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%20had%20secured%20the%20Hajipur%20seat%20eight%20times%2C%20with%20four%20consecutive%20victories%20starting%20in%201996.%20In%20the%202024%20polls%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%20won%20the%20seat%20by%20over%201.7%20lakh%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20lost%20everything%20-%20the%20party%2C%20the%20symbol%2C%20the%20organisation%2C%20and%20the%20house%20we%20stayed%20in%20for%20three%20decades.%20So%20everything%20was%20taken%20away%20from%20me.%20I%20had%20to%20start%20from%20scratch%3B%20I%20did%20not%20even%20know%20how%20to%20make%20a%20new%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20Chirag%20Paswan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20LJP%20spli