href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswiss-vs-american-parenting-differences-independence-freedom-culture-shock-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20lot%20of%20independence%20as%20a%20child%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20age%204%20or%205%2C%20I%20was%20leaving%20the%20house%20alone%20to%20walk%20around%20the%20neighborhood%20and%20meet%20up%20with%20my%20friends.%20We%20lived%20right%20next%20to%20a%20forest%20in%20Oslo%20and%20often%20played%20there%20in%20the%20afternoons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20local%20kids%20in%20Bali%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edo%20that%2C%20too%2C%20but%20it's%20harder%20to%20get%20around%20Bali%20on%20foot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20aren't%20many%20proper%20sidewalks%2C%20and%20kids%20have%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-couple-moved-city-bali-things-they-learned-tips-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewatch%20out%20for%20traffic%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20now%2C%20my%20kids%20are%20too%20young%20to%20go%20out%20on%20their%20own%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b560c0b-a892-4bb8-89c1-42a9df9dc071%5C%22%3EI've%20noticed%20that%20Asian%20families%20seem%20closer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20parents%20often%20sleep%20with%20their%20young%20kids%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20In%20Norway%2C%20it's%20common%20to%20do%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-to-start-sleep-training-your-newborn%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esleep%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20let%20the%20kid%20cry%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tried%20that%20with%20our%20children%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20feel%20right.%20Now%2C%20even%20though%20we%20don't%20get%20much%20sleep%2C%20we%20still%20sleep%20together%20as%20a%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kids'%20sleeping%20area.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66729788087acd2be9b4e4c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%2