%200.73%20bags%20mishandled%20per%20100%20bags%20enplaned%2C%20respectively.%20Delta%20was%20the%20best-performing%20of%20the%20three%2C%20with%20a%20rate%20of%200.47.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20cases%2C%20the%20ticket%20can%20be%20upgraded%20to%20regular%20coach%20for%20things%20like%20an%20assigned%20seat%20and%20no%20change%20fees.%20I'd%20recommend%20paying%20up%20if%20you%20want%20a%20little%20more%20control%20over%20your%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOut%20of%20the%20three%20discount%20options%2C%20American%20and%20Delta%20often%20offer%20more%20bang%20for%20your%20buck%20than%20United's%20more%20restrictive%20basic%20fares.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20is%20holding%20a%20boarding%20pass%20with%20the%20flight%20information%20and%20%26quot%3Bno%20carry-on%26quot%3B%20written%20in%20big%20letters%20across%20the%20top.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668ff9d639de72f47bca3ffa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUnited's%20boarding%20pass%20made%20it%20crystal%20clear%20that%20I%20was%20not%20allowed%20a%20carry-on%20bag%20with%20my%20basic%20economy%20ticket.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20point%20of%20basic%20economy%20is%20to%20lure%20in%20price-sensitive%20travelers%20(like%20me)%20with%20a%20fare%20that%20only%20requires%20you%20to%20pay%20for%20what%20you%20need.%20It's%20basically%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflying-ultra-low-cost-airlines-spirit-frontier-not-worth-it-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow-cost%20model%20but%20with%20the%20perks%20of%20mainline%20cabins%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20inflight%20entertainment%2C%20free%20snacks%2C%20and%20reclining%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20American%20and%20Delta%2C%20United%20made%20its%20offer%20as%20barebones%20as%20possible%20by%20not%20allowing%20carry-on%20bags%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExcept%20for%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.united.com%2Fen%2Fus%2Ffly%2Ftravel%2Finflight%2Fbasic-economy.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternational%3C%2Fa%3E%20routes%2C%20anything%20more%20than%20a%20personal%20item%20on%20United%20has%20to%20be%20checked.%20Delta%20and%20American%20allow%20a%20carry-on%20and%20a%20personal%20item%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20seat%20rule%20is%20the%20same%20across%20the%20board%20%E2%80%94%20you%20pay%20extra%20to%20reserve%20one.%20Otherwise%2C%20you'll%20get%20a%20random%20seat%20at%20check-in%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20ended%20up%20with%20a%20middle%20seat%20on%20every%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUnited's%20policy%20required%20me%20to%20spend%20an%20extra%20%2440%20to%20check%20my%20carry-on%2C%20which%20isn't%20ideal%20and%20could%20be%20a%20dealbreaker%20if%20a%20competitor%20is%20cheaper.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221148%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20American%2C%20Delta%2C%20and%20United%20flights%20showing%20%2456%20one-way%20from%20NYC%20to%20Chicago%20O'Hare%20on%20Oct%2016%20on%20Google%20Flights.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6697e16c5439fb59cebe2638%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22574%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20Flights%20shows%20the%20same%20price%20for%20all%20three%20mainlines%20from%20LaGuardia%20to%20Chicago%20on%20October%2016%2C%20but%20you%20won't%20get%20a%20carry-on%20bag%20on%20United.%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Flights%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20a%20one-way%20basic%20economy%20flight%20from%20LaGuardia%20to%20Chicago%20in%20mid-October%20is%20%2456%20on%20American%2C%20Delta%2C%20and%20United%2C%20according%20to%20Google%20Flights.%20Other%20dates%20show%20similarly%20close%20fares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20added%20fee%20and%20hassle%20of%20checking%20a%20bag%20on%20United%2C%20I'd%20book%20one%20of%20the%20other%20two%20by%20probably%20flipping%20a%20coin%20since%20I%20simply%20don't%20care%20about%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhile%20the%20no%20carry-on%20bothered%20me%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20problem%20for%20everyone.%20United%20earns%20points%20for%20its%20more%20tech-savvy%20cabin.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20seatback%20screen%20saying%20the%20Bluetooth%20connected%20to%20the%20author's%20Beats%20headphones.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668ffef039de72f47bca4269%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20travel%20with%20overhead%20Beats%20headphones%20and%20AirPods%2C%20but%20I%20prefer%20the%20Beats%20and%20can%20connect%20them%20to%20United's%20economy%20cabin.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20plane%20I%20flew%20on%20was%20retrofitted%20with%20the%20airline's%20enhanced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflying-on-united-airlines-in-2021-during-pandemic-photos-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BUnited%20Next%26quot%3B%20cabin%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20unveiled%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20offers%20the%20regular%20bells%20and%20whistles%20you'll%20find%20on%20most%20American%20and%20Delta%20narrowbodies%2C%20but%20you%20can%20also%20connect%20Bluetooth%20headphones%20to%20the%20seatback%20screens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20much%20better%20option%20than%20using%20regular%20earbuds%2C%20especially%20if%20you're%20stuck%20with%20the%20scratchy%20airline-provided%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYou'll%20get%20a%20similar%20cabin%20layout%20on%20Delta%2C%20but%20without%20Bluetooth%2C%20unless%20you're%20in%20first%20class%20on%20an%20A321neo.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223948%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Delta%20inflight%20television%20screen%20with%20the%20A220-100%20aircraft%20on%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%