sassination%20attempt%20means%20it%20is%20game%2C%20set%2C%20match%20for%20Trump%20in%20the%20November%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20particular%20event%2C%20the%20assassination%20attempt%2C%20has%20practically%20sealed%20the%20election%20campaign.%20It%20is%20almost%20over.%20It%20is%20very%20challenging%20at%20this%20point%20for%20Democrats%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20to%20do.%20Such%20a%20contrast%20has%20been%20laid%20out%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20electorate.%20Two%20weeks%20prior%20to%20this%2C%20you%20had%20this%20debate%20between%20Trump%20and%20Biden%20where%20everybody%20recognises%2C%20including%20president%20Biden%2C%20that%20it%20was%20really%20a%20bad%20night%20for%20him.%20He%20just%20seemed%20to%20be%20lost.%20He%20didn't%20seem%20to%20be%20anywhere%3B%20could%20not%20answer%20any%20question.%20Sleepy%20Joe%20as%20he%20has%20been%20known%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Republican%20Hindu%20Coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20contrast%20to%20that%20we%20have%20a%20man%20of%20steel%2C%20a%20fighter.%20Doesn't%20look%20like%20a%2078-year-old.%20After%20getting%20shot%20in%20his%20right%20ear%2C%20if%20he%20had%20been%20looking%20straight%20it%20would%20have%20gone%20straight%20to%20his%20head.%20He%20gets%20up%20and%20has%20this%20fighting%20spirit%2C%20says%20fight%2C%20fight%2C%20fight.%20That's%20what%20Americans%20like%20to%20see%20in%20their%20presidents.%20As%20it%20stands%20right%20now%2C%20unless%20the%20Democrats%20come%20up%20with%20a%20different%20candidate%2C%20they%20still%20have%20a%20month%20to%20go%2C%20this%20election%20is%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20prominent%20Indian-American%20businessman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPressed%20to%20answer%20if%20there%20is%20a%20rethink%20on%20the%20presidential%20candidate%20on%20the%20Democratic%20side%2C%20he%20said%20he%20is%20hoping%20for%20a%20last-minute%20change%20to%20make%20for%20an%20exciting%20contest.%20They%20still%20have%20a%20month%20to%20decide%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20still%20betting%20on%20President%20Barack%20Obama%20convincing%20his%20wife%20Michelle%20Obama%20to%20step%20in%20at%20the%20last%20minute.%20Then%20there%20would%20be%20a%20real%20contest.%20I%20would%20probably%20say%20then%20between%20Trump%20and%20Michelle%20Obama%20there%20will%20be%20a%20contest.%20Between%20Trump%20and%20Joe%20Biden%20there%20is%20no%20contest.%20Between%20Trump%20and%20Kamala%20Harris%20there%20is%20no%20contest.%20Behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20everybody%20wishes%20on%20the%20Democrat%20part%20that%20Michelle%20Obama%20is%20persuaded%20to%20become%20the%20Democrat%20nominee.%20A%20good%20contest%20is%20always%20a%20good%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20man%2C%20who%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20Ronald%20Reagan%20re-election%20campaign%20in%201984.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20to%20come%20up%20with%20something%20different.%20I%20am%20hoping%20Obama%20convinces%20Michelle%20to%20step%20up.%20Then%20there%20will%20be%20a%20real%20contest.%20They%20have%20to%20find%20somebody%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20businessman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20the%20fundraising%20is%20coming%20along%20post%20the%20assassination%20attempt%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20it%20has%20seen%20a%20dramatic%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoney%20is%20going%20like%20crazy.%20Donor%20class%20is%20seeing%20that%20the%20DJT%20(Donald%20John%20Trump)%20is%20coming%20back%20as%20the%2047th%20president.%20Am%20sure%20you%20are%20aware%20of%20what%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20done.%20%2445%20million%20a%20month%20till%20the%20election.%20Peter%20Thiel.%20Big%20time%20people%20are%20coming%20forward%20and%20funding%20the%20campaign.%20Money%20raising%20has%20increased%20dramatically%20after%20the%20assassination%20attempt%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20businessman%20who%20is%20not%20just%20a%20financial%20backer%20but%20is%20on%20the%20ground%20getting%20people%20out%20to%20vote%20