nto%20the%20podium%2C%20surrounding%20him%20and%20rushing%20him%20to%20a%20nearby%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIconic%20images%20of%20a%20bloodied%20Trump%20waving%20his%20fist%20after%20the%20shooting%20are%20already%20galvanizing%20Republican%20hopes%20that%20voters%20will%20further%20rally%20behind%20him%20for%20a%20landslide%20victory%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20campaign%20after%20the%20assassination%20attempt%20has%20become%20a%20different%20campaign.%20It's%20altogether%20different.%20The%20enthusiasm%20in%20the%20delegates%20and%20people%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20the%20MAGA%20crowd%2C%20the%20enthusiasm%20is%20through%20the%20roof.%20As%20everybody%20can%20sense%20that%20at%20this%20point%20in%20time%2C%20unless%20a%20miracle%20happens%20for%20Democrats%2C%20he%20is%20the%2047th%20president%20of%20the%20US%20and%20we%20are%20all%20very%20happy%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721245680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fvua35aao_shalabh-kumar-ndtv_625x300_18_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fassassination-attempt-has-sealed-the-election-donald-trump-close-aide-shalabh-kumar-to-ndtv-6128460%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Unless%20a%20miracle%20happens%20for%20Democrats%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20set%20to%20be%20the%2047th%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%2C%20a%20beaming%20Shalabh%20Kumar%2C%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20Trump%2C%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fassassination-attempt-has-sealed-the-election-donald-trump-close-aide-shalabh-kumar-to-ndtv-6128460%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fassassination-attempt-has-sealed-the-election-donald-trump-close-aide-shalabh-kumar-to-ndtv-6128460%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F