0With%20HIV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20Mangal%20Shah%20from%20Maharashtra%20found%20two%20HIV%2B%20babies%20aged%202.5%20and%201.5%20years%2C%20abandoned%20in%20a%20dirty%20cow%20shed.%20The%20children%20were%20left%20there%2C%20believed%20to%20have%20brought%20%E2%80%98shame%E2%80%99%20to%20their%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20found%20no%20orphanage%20willing%20to%20accept%20them%2C%20she%20brought%20them%20home.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20disheartened%20to%20see%20that%20no%20government%20hospital%20was%20ready%20to%20admit%20them.%20We%20also%20tried%20to%20contact%20NGOs%20for%20orphans%2C%20but%20they%20also%20turned%20them%20away%20because%20of%20their%20HIV%20status.%20So%2C%20instead%20of%20waiting%20around%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20care%20of%20these%20two%20little%20girls%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20experience%20inspired%20her%20to%20launch%20the%20Palawi%20Project%20to%20provide%20a%20loving%20home%20for%20such%20children.%20Fondly%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263134%2Fmaharashtra-free-hiv-aids-care-home-orphan-children-palawi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMangal%20%3Cem%3Etai%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E(elder%20sister%20in%20Marathi)%2C%20she%20now%20extends%20motherly%20care%20to%20over%20150%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F216760%2Findia-hiv-children-adoption-social-awareness-national-award-karnataka-inspiring-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHIV%2B%20children%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9cqAa4oOHC%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campai