ery%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPhysically%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20follow%20a%20strict%20fitness%20routine%20but%20occasionally%20hit%20the%20gym.%20Our%20bodies%20have%20adapted%20to%20long%20rides%2C%20making%20biking%20more%20comfortable%20than%20long%20car%20journeys.%20The%20connection%20with%20our%20bike%20has%20developed%20over%20time%2C%20making%20long-distance%20rides%20manageable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Three%20Magic%20Words%3A%C2%A0%20Plan%2C%20Plan%20%26amp%3B%20Plan!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20planning%20their%20first%20long-distance%20bike%20trip%2C%20thorough%20planning%20is%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStart%20with%20shorter%20distances%2C%20covering%20200-300%20km%20per%20day%2C%20and%20gradually%20increase%20as%20you%20become%20more%20comfortable.%20Consider%20the%20road%20conditions%20and%20weather%2C%20especially%20in%20hilly%20areas.%20Investing%20in%20a%20riding%20class%20can%20be%20beneficial%2C%20teaching%20you%20how%20to%20handle%20various%20terrains%20and%20unexpected%20situations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBook%20your%20accommodations%20ahead%20of%20time.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20book%20accommodations%20through%20platforms%20like%20MMT%2C%20Booking.com%2C%20and%20Airbnb%2C%20and%20sometimes%20collaborate%20with%20properties%20if%20they%20have%20approved%20for%20a%20partnership%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20What%20not%20to%20do%20on%20long%20travels%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommon%20mistakes%20new%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F314699%2Fbengaluru-startup-electric-motorcycle-bike-expedition-trip-across-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebike%20travellers%3C%2Fa%3E%20make%20include%20underestimating%20the%20importance%20of%20preparation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2