0states%20in%20the%20country.%20In%20Chandigarh%2C%20we%20are%20required%20to%20maintain%20a%20temperature%20between%2020%20and%2026%20degrees%20and%20humidity%20of%2060%20to%2065%20percent.%20These%20parameters%20can%20be%20different%20for%20Kashmir.%20We%20need%20to%20first%20analyse%20the%20geography%2C%20climate%2C%20and%20weather%20conditions%2C%20and%20accordingly%20design%20and%20set%20up%20the%20farm%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Pritpal%20also%20started%20Farmcult%2C%20a%20bootstrapped%20Agritech%20startup%20providing%20end-to-end%20solutions%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20enter%20the%20world%20of%20hydroponics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmcult%20currently%20operates%20under%20two%20business%20models%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1%3A%20%3Cstrong%3ETurnkey%20Projects%20and%20Consulting%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Farmcult%20designs%20and%20sets%20up%20modern%C2%A0%20hydroponic%20farms%2C%20customised%20according%20to%20the%20geographical%20location%20and%20the%20crop%20to%20be%20cultivated.%20They%20not%20only%20set%20up%20the%20farms%2C%20but%20also%20support%20their%20clients%20for%20at%20least%20six%20months%2C%20ensuring%20they%20are%20comfortable%20with%20every%20aspect%20of%20the%20hydroponics%20business.%20Farmcult%20also%20helps%20establish%20market%20linkages%20for%20the%20crops%20being%20cultivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-2-1721052208.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pritpal%20aspires%20to%20encourage%20more%20people%20to%20adopt%20hydroponics.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-2-1721052208.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-2-1721052208-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebet