%20are%20the%20drivers%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20next%20economic%20wave.%20The%20contest%20called%20for%20entries%20from%20across%20the%20country%20of%20people%20who%20are%20turning%20their%20dreams%20and%20aspirations%20into%20reality%20by%20doing%20a%20range%20of%20things%2C%20from%20starting%20businesses%20to%20innovating%20in%20everyday%20life%2C%20thus%20bringing%20financial%20growth%20to%20their%20households.%20Storytellers%20from%20all%20corners%20of%20India%20joined%20in%20and%20the%20contest%20provided%20them%20with%20the%20stage%20to%20bring%20the%20struggles%20and%20victories%20of%20Entrepreneurial%20Households%20(a%20term%20coined%20by%20Enmasse)%20to%20light.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20are%20Entrepreneurial%20Households%3F%20You%E2%80%99ll%20recognise%20them%20as%20savvy%2C%20business-minded%2C%20resilient%20households%20with%20multiple%20income%20streams%20and%20strategic%20borrowings%2C%20all%20leveraged%20for%20growth%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20them%20all%20around%20you%2C%20and%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20of%20the%20contest%2C%20thus%2C%20was%20to%20send%20out%20a%20clear%20message%20that%20these%20homes%20are%20no%20longer%20a%20sidenote%20in%20the%20margins.%20They%20hold%20the%20transformative%20power%20to%20shape%20the%20future%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20contest%20like%20this%20provides%20the%20opportunity%20for%20existing%20and%20new%20entrepreneurs%20and%20business%20leaders%20to%20move%20the%20gaze%20away%20from%20big%20cities%20and%20disposable%20incomes%20to%20small%20towns%20and%20core%20services%2C%20and%20they%E2%80%99ll%20find%20that%20the%20market%20potential%20is%20immense.%20Enmasse%20World%20calls%20this%20the%20Economic%20Power%20of%20Industrious%20Communities%2C%20or%20the%20EPIC%20Opportunity.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C