f%20opening%20a%20junior%20high%20school%20in%20the%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ghosh%20secured%20the%20approvals%20in%202010%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20school%20did%20not%20start%20until%202014.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20know%20how%20government%20work%20is%20%E2%80%94%20slow%20as%20a%20snail.%20I%20dedicated%20all%20my%20time%20to%20getting%20the%20construction%20process%20started.%20The%20ruling%20party%20leaders%20at%20the%20time%20did%20not%20support%20me%20at%20all%2C%20but%20I%20had%20strong%20faith%20that%20everything%20would%20work%20out.%20Eventually%2C%20when%20the%20construction%20did%20start%2C%20it%20was%20the%20poor%20people%20of%20the%20village%20who%20helped%20me%20complete%20it%20quickly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhosh%20faced%20another%20challenge%20when%20the%20school%20needed%20permanent%20teachers%20appointed.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20been%20struggling%20with%20no%20permanent%20teachers%20for%20years.%20Back%20then%2C%20I%20was%20faced%20with%20a%20dilemma%20%E2%80%94%20if%20I%20left%20the%20school%20without%20any%20permanent%20teacher%2C%20it%20would%20shut%20down.%20I%20have%20been%20working%20without%20a%20salary%20ever%20since%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-21-1720614806.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ghosh%20has%20been%20teaching%20for%20free%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20now.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-21-1720614806.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-21-1720614806-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-21-1720614806-500x262.jpg