encroaching-on-whose-space%20prevails%2C%20farmers%20in%20regions%20like%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Gujarat%20face%20heavy%20losses%20due%20to%20animal%20encroachment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20innovations%20to%20keep%20animals%20at%20bay%20have%20been%20developed%20by%20companies%20all%20across%20the%20country%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20who%20aim%20at%20scaring%20the%20animals%20away%20without%20the%20intention%20of%20hurting%20them.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKatidhan%20aims%20to%20help%20farmers%20mitigate%20their%20losses%20while%20keeping%20the%20animals%20at%20a%20distance.%20We%20study%20their%20movements%20and%20use%20technology%20to%20scare%20the%20animals%20from%20human%20settlements%2C%E2%80%9D%20S%20R%20Ayan%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20startup%2C%20shares%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKatidhan%20helps%20farmers%20reduce%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F232462%2Fifs-hero-elephant-safety-fence-electric-uttarakhand-haldwani-man-animal-elephant-conflict-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20wildlife-related%20losses%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20their%20innovative%20products%20aimed%20at%20a%20harmless%20resolution%20of%20such%20conflicts.%20The%20startup%20was%20also%20featured%20on%20a%20Shark%20Tank%20episode%20in%20season%203%2C%20bagging%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%201.5%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInnovations%20that%20do%20not%20harm%20the%20animals%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20Bengaluru%2C%20Ayan%20is%20a%20robotics%20engineer%20who%20worked%20on%20building%20consumer%20robots.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20working%20in%20the%20city%20when%20a%20friend%20highlighted%20the%20issue%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F